Calm down, everyone. Posts are ussually slow during the weekend, its no big 
deal.

::Mosquitor::

The CR chamber opens, a foot emerging. It sets itself on the ground, along 
with it's owner's other foot, as Mosquitor steps out. Mosquitor looks around, 
a bit dazed. For a second, he thought he was standing upside down inside 
someone's head, but that thought vanished as soon as he looked back at the CR 
chambers. As far as he knew, bots' heads did not contain CR chambers. But 
other places did....

Mosquitor frowns, thinking of all the places that could have CR chambers. 
Shoes? No, those wern't big enough. Maybe guns! He looks down at his gun, 
finally deciding it was too small to hold a CR chamber.

He frowns again. It was nagging at him, the place that has CR chambers, but 
he couldn't put his finger on it. It started with a 'B'... Bugs? No. 
Mosquitor shakes his head, deep in thought over this complicated problem. 
Booms? No, that was a sound, sounds can't hold objects, and CR chambers were 
an object. Bats? Mosquitor grinds his teeth in frustration. That was close, 
but no.

His eyes light up as the answer hits him. BASE! Yes, that was it! He must be 
in the Predacon base! In the CR room! A smile stretches across Mosquitor's 
face as the idiot bug walks out of the room, proud of his brilliant deducing 
skills.
